{"tid":1949212,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"為咗張八達通搞分化","createTime":"2020-03-29T13:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T14:39:47.000Z","uid":151610,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9c33f0147c7baff6afc5e82465886d7660739a20","tid":1949212,"uid":151610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:12:18.000Z","msg":"文長慎入<br />\n<br />\n有位F小姐 唔見咗張八達通 <br />\n就係FB谷同WhatsApp谷到 嘈咗兩日半<br />\n22/3 16:59 F小姐係&quot;沙田之友&quot;開post話自己唔見八達通<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/637034979770255/permalink/1706051692868573/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F637034979770255%2Fpermalink%2F1706051692868573%2F&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=d5300ff6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/637034979770255/permalink/1706051692868573/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTQumFE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTQumFE.png&h=d1eb9ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lt;留意返F小姐 係話18/3晚唔咗張八達通 但係22/3先發現&gt;<br />\nPost完FB之後同一日(22/3 17:17)就去whatsapp谷到開post<br />\n<br />\n其實F小姐放上FB到既資料同WhatsApp上既資料<br />\n大概一樣 係人都估到係同一個人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4gpU1h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4gpU1h.png&h=39a0a0c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內容大致上同FB一模一樣既<br />\n仲要係23/3 凌晨3:00 send張盜竊罪既法例出黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rtM5Ete.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrtM5Ete.png&h=e3497c9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實想點呢?<br />\n為咗張八達通嘈兩日為咩？<br />\n<br />\n想人幫手搵個小偷 其他人就叫佢報警, cut卡<br />\n佢覺得冇人想幫手搵就打算屈係個谷嘅人偷左<br />\n仲話比次機會人改過自身。。。<br />\n黃谷到搵藍人(去完A1又去吉野家唔係藍唔通黃咩)玩咩？<br />\n有人問佢有無咩證據指控<br />\n就即時改口話係叫人幫佢留意, 又叫人幫佢睇cctv<br />\n<br />\n有爬文嘅谷友就好心講解比啲冇爬文嘅谷友知咩事<br />\n自然要講埋來龍去脈再分析返個位F小姐<br />\n明明公開既FB自爆6月開始冇返工<br />\n又要係個人FB度公開post自己開咗鋪頭做老闆娘<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fioli\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffioli&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=2ce29631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fioli</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/819fhfw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F819fhfw.png&h=107ea623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後FB&quot;沙田之友&quot;既谷就有個分化post<br />\n歪理變真理 好過份離晒譜 <br />\n(&quot;沙田之友&quot;入谷問題答藍同黃都可以入谷, 個谷係藍係黃 自己諗啦)<br />\n<br />\nVenus Siu公審個WhatsApp谷<br />\n成篇野冇頭冇尾post少少嘢出黎加鹽加醋就話有證據<br />\n完全冇講個起因係乜就屈人虛黃, 藍變黃, 又話冇言論自由<br />\n人地要你拎證據出黎, 你就話唔post咁多住<br />\n即係到底你有無證據?<br />\n(利申: 我本身喺個Whatsapp谷度, 但極少講野<br />\n睇番原來成件事係因為一個人唔見八達通就搞到咁？)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有睇晒FB留言既人都知完全唔存在F小姐比人起底<br />\n仲要屈谷友起事主底? 柒少陣啦!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RgrmcPB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgrmcPB.png&h=edcd9031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/shUCvBg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FshUCvBg.png&h=d0b20665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n補充返 Chung Gary真身係Venus Siu<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pkchunggary\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpkchunggary&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=d73ba2f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pkchunggary</a><br />\n<br />\nWhatsapp admin 用咗Venus Siu做谷名<br />\n迫個分化撚出黎 <br />\n佢唔甘心 就改名同冒認自己係 Chung Gary<br />\n(而黎個Venus Siu好明顯就有人黎個whatsapp谷入面)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最爆點 你話自己冇起group入面個兩admin底<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jXr9mJm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjXr9mJm.png&h=9a5dd4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LS8cjvn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLS8cjvn.png&h=ac21ad09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ncap WhatsApp對話特登唔遮人哋既電話號碼 <br />\n一味係到老屈人<br />\n&lt;原本個圖冇遮電話號碼既 利申 係本人自己遮&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTmM8oX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTmM8oX.png&h=13077778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍絲依家仲會講&lsquo;專業暴徒&lsquo;咩？<br />\n唔係叫&rsquo;專業曱甴&rsquo;咩？<br />\n睇黎未識分藍絲同黃絲仲話自己係金黃🤣<br />\n你咁叫正義幫朋友吖？叫人收口但自己仲講緊  <br />\n你除咗係分化撚+阻膠之外 仲係一個是非精!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我建議大家上&quot;沙田之友&quot;谷到睇埋其他既精彩既留言<br />\n利申 圖太多唔cap<br />\n<br />\nFiona Li你話自己有辦法睇到cctv <br />\n咁本事睇到cctv就自己去搵人啦<br />\n仲有個爆笑點<br />\n見到吉野家 a1麵包店之後 <br />\n就知執咗八達通條友係藍啦<br />\n入黃谷搵藍人<br />\n你都算係經典喇!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFiona li<br />\nVenus Siu<br />\n做人柒左就算啦, 收手啦"},{"pid":"9a93af6e5ed53a643149ccd3f8d39fe7188cbfa4","tid":1949212,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:13:57.000Z","msg":"[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"658e0e1a6dd2a0539d56a949325d46f0f11596bf","tid":1949212,"uid":151610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:23:51.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"af03bdaaa2f890029a8de6965329dfcf0406e0f8","tid":1949212,"uid":151610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb9e8e4b46c7c401891ce39c7e4e9f665c99998","tid":1949212,"uid":151610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:39:08.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"7c84ad3c2ba436c258ccf9b145a21810836e4104","tid":1949212,"uid":151610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:39:29.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"0fba111f6e4216f179c82f273513d489aae8fa01","tid":1949212,"uid":151610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:39:47.000Z","msg":"沙田分化撚"}]}